reviewText: I don't see how this DVD could be improved!  Esther carried Abraham's dynamics magnificently throughout the whole presentation.  Though the Martin Luther King segment will probably become a classic, there were several other equally pointed moments in this DVD.  As most of you have discovered, each DVD contains nuggets of information that are distinct to that DVD, but if you can only afford one, this is the one I would recommend.  Blessings to you and Gratitude to Abraham-Hicks.  Carena del Uno
